snippet.textDisplay:
I’m a nerd so i did this.
Using the high end, I calculated how much a full inventory of emerald blocks would cost, and also how much it would weigh. but here you go.

A single Minecraft emerald is worth $11,587,500,000
So One emerald block would be worth $104,287,500,000
A stack of blocks would be worth $6,674,400,000,000
This means that a full inventory of emerald blocks is worth $240,278,400,000,000.

And...

An emerald alone is 680 pounds.
A block of emerald is 6,128 pounds.
392,192 pounds for a stack of emerald blocks.
Meaning a Full inventory weighs 14,118,912 pounds.

Sorry for wasting your time with random knowledge.
